      "layout": "The page maintains a contained layout with a maximum width of 1320px, usually centered. The hero section features a dominant centered headline over a dark, full-width background. Content sections beneath follow a structured rhythm, often alternating between a light page canvas and the dark Midnight Indigo card surfaces. Elements are frequently stacked vertically, with the potential for grid-based arrangements for features. Navigation is a persistent top bar, with elements neatly spaced.",
